ll, always open extra late and welcoming to my late arrival. Located directly across the street from 6 Columbus is the Time Warner Center, a luxury shopping venue. Close to subways, Columbus Circle and Central Park made 6 Columbus a Thompson Hotel to be envied by all Manhattan boutique Hotels.Yes, I will stay there again. Thank you 6 Columbus.	
